{"tid":1620352,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"點解條例唔即時生效？要凌晨生效？擺明係局呀！","createTime":"2019-10-04T10:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T11:31:11.000Z","uid":5960,"like":9,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"61f45aa6b6e37720a063b40c6c2059df5a71f115","tid":1620352,"uid":5960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:08:17.000Z","msg":"點解條例唔即時生效？要凌晨生效？就係因為想引你地出曬去，然後拉幾百人。<br />\n<br />\n依家又去紅隧又改道，我相信地鐵、巴士入黑後好快會停，到時又會變左冇交通嘅大圍捕。<br />\n<br />\n各位手足聽我講，依家香港各局已經有大量兵力準備好拉人，大家唔好為左一時之氣今晚出去比人拉！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求  缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21dc2abf193b0805505887cd9f9dcbfac2acd4d9","tid":1620352,"uid":5960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:09:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5a2a87683c9bbb16162241ef42ddc6a3333c4c5","tid":1620352,"uid":137204,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:10:38.000Z","msg":"都係果句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出嚟打仗 自備後路</span>"},{"pid":"ca918cbd3e268f1dd2c8cd9d5df079aa0774f14c","tid":1620352,"uid":67505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:11:58.000Z","msg":"冇交通咪18區開花咯"},{"pid":"2278e2f557f826c4975d29259d614ae26be557e0","tid":1620352,"uid":325108,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:15:14.000Z","msg":"出左蒙面法嘅結果<br />\n<br />\n更多人出黎嘅話，就大條道理再運用緊急法升級<br />\n<br />\n少咗人出黎，又達到佢想要嘅效果<br />\n<br />\n公就佢贏，字就香港人輸"},{"pid":"94095de81212d0d55b8e57bd01e42d59d7b2dcc0","tid":1620352,"uid":67043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:43:06.000Z","msg":"咁驚你自己留係屋企啦"},{"pid":"938a26504845739bd2b5416ecb5045772b5bc4c8","tid":1620352,"uid":5960,"like":0,"dislike":